basics.label: IT Manager
basics.summary: Experienced IT Manager with a focus on system availability, infrastructure upgrades, and problem resolution. Skilled in multiple systems such as Windows Server, Cisco, and Linux, while also managing corporate networks and databases.

work.name: Company Name
work.summary: Stabilize and manage infrastructure and applications for corporate and remote facilities. Work with various departments to determine technology needs. Perform regular security audits of internal infrastructure and applications.
highlights: Managed corporate website and necessary edits
Implemented Voice Over Internet Protocol Phone System for entire organization

work.name: Company Name
work.summary: Managed a team of help desk technicians to ensure excellent customer satisfaction and prompt issue resolution for over 30 clients
highlights: Maintained consistent communications with client point of contact
Formulated monthly help desk budget and managed accordingly
